Football Association of Malaysia (FAM) has appointed Spanish coach Javier Jorda Ribera as head coach of U17 Malaysia.
Javier, who is also the Director of Johor Darul Ta'zim Football Academy, will lead the Malaysia U17 team to participate in the 2024 AFF U-16 Championship in Jakarta, Indonesia and the 2025 AFC U-17 Asian Cup Qualifiers.
